This suggestion outlines the significance of maintaining a backup power source alongside your solar system to ensure consistent energy availability.<br><br>

1. <b>Importance of Backup Power</b> - While solar systems are designed to provide renewable energy, there are circumstances where additional power may be necessary. These circumstances include:<br>
<ul>
<li data-lh-list>Prolonged periods of cloudy weather</li>
<li data-lh-list>System maintenance or faults</li>
<li data-lh-list>Unexpected outages</li>
